{"id": 1701, "genre": 1000, "title": "你的哪些消费升级其实主要是包装升级？", "description": "不太会认真去比对成分效果，做决断时主要还是考虑可承受范围内瓶子最好看的…包装是如何影响你的消费行为的？选项里没有的话，欢迎在评论里补充个人经验。", "record_count": 10471, "comment_count": 29, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170524125602fY2oh4EM93XuA78I.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-05-25T17:00:29Z", "questions": [{"id": 2349, "title": "你的哪些消费升级其实主要是包装升级？", "content": "你的哪些消费升级其实主要是包装升级？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 206746, "content": "日常买瓶装饮料，味道差别不大，但要瓶子好看的", "image": "img/option/option/201705241210093JaXcYRrWfM092gT.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 206748, "content": "升级洗衣液洗手液洗洁精，也是尽量挑包装清爽的", "image": "img/option/option/20170524122000nZjI1GmfT7btuwBS.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 206750, "content": "护肤品化妆品沐浴用品，淘汰了花里胡哨版", "image": "img/option/option/201705251447153haxerFSuGoBCO6g.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 206751, "content": "尝试的新零食，也要追求muji感包装", "image": "img/option/option/20170524122252bL0XjEzIB4nhQrSR.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 206752, "content": "想买的书两个版本，一般不看价格，看谁的装帧素雅点", "image": "img/option/option/20170524122507Sx9H1lEXrN0PDpnT.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 206754, "content": "老字号的传统包装嫌太丑，但如果出了牛皮纸袋包装就可以", "image": "img/option/option/20170524124538MJAUXrn0hw6B5cLV.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 206756, "content": "茶叶压缩袋装的感觉像我爸的style，有好看的铁罐装就想买", "image": "img/option/option/20170524152012QPUmROj0hLcpWfC4.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 206757, "content": "厨具，铝制的看着就像宾馆的，一定要买马卡龙色", "image": "img/option/option/20170524152037fhIETNLbyXwAePkg.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}